track_notes: SS-125 and SS-167 - here is a walk submitted on behalf of Terry G0VWP who activated these two summits in April 2014.
track_title: Long circuit taking taking in Scald Law  Black Hill

track_notes:
A short but steep walk from the 101 bus stop (Edinburgh to Dumfries) to the summit. Steep enough to need a hand on the ground to help climb in places. Some loose stones underfoot as well.

The path is mostly clear. Just follow the valley up to the ridge line then walk to the trig point.
track_title: Steep climb from Silverburn Bus Stop to Scald Law

track_notes: From parking on the A702. The return route from Black Hill followed the Quad Bike track and the main path to go up and over to the A702. Moving time 3hrs total day 6hrs.
